# Deploy — solo-law

## Actions taken

### mw-backend
- Committed: `solo_law_blueprint.py` (new, 681 lines) + `server.py` (blueprint registration)
- Pushed to `main` → Surface auto-deploy pulled + restarted Flask
- Verified after ~35s:
  - `api.michaelwegter.com/health` → `{"status":"ok","version":"1.0.0"}` ✓
  - `api.michaelwegter.com/solo-law/health` → `{"ok":true,"service":"solo-law"}` ✓

### michaelwegter.com
- Committed: `public/demos/solo-law/` (30 files: Angular chunks, i18n assets, webllm-worker.js) + `src/data/workSamples.js`
- Pushed to `main` → GH Pages auto-deployed
- Verified:
  - `https://michaelwegter.com/demos/solo-law/` → HTTP 200 ✓
  - `/work-samples` → 404 (expected SPA behavior, 404.html redirect handles it) ✓

### CORS
- `Origin: https://michaelwegter.com` against `api.michaelwegter.com/solo-law/health`
