## handoff
- produced: both repos pushed and live; Flask blueprint serving at /solo-law/*, demo at /demos/solo-law/ (200), CORS confirmed from michaelwegter.com origin
- decisions: /work-samples 404 is SPA behavior (expected), not a defect; no backend seed step needed (blueprint seeds on first request)
- next needs: deploy-test must exercise CMS login (editor@solo-law.demo / Demo2026!), locale switch (EN/ES/FR), and at least one live API call (practice-areas or publications) from the deployed origin
- risks: WebLLM/WebGPU agentic AI requires a WebGPU-capable browser — may be absent in headless Playwright; test should fall back to mock mode gracefully (confirmed in build)
